                <head>No. 618.<lb/>
                    <hi rend="italic">General <persName type="from">Sickles</persName> to Mr.
                            <persName type="to">Fish</persName>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1873-11-16">
                            <hi rend="italic">November</hi> 16, 1873</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Layard informs me he has received instructions from his government concerning
                    seventeen British subjects among the crew of the Vir-ginius executed, and seven
                    more under sentence of death, the latter all minors. Of the seventeen dead, six
                    were executed immediately on the arrival of the Virginius in port. A British
                    frigate is ordered to Santiago.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>SICKLES.</signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
